{"tid":1142663,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"黃秋生：分紅好過收片酬","createTime":"2019-05-07T08:22:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-07T12:03:27.000Z","uid":134071,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8dd7255e8d49b2c7091c074d873e5f6834848717","tid":1142663,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T08:22:24.000Z","msg":"唔奇.    記得成龍以前拍嘉朱既戲, 話如果嘉禾願意增加分紅百分率, 佢拍戲唔收片酬都無問題. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"http://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/%E9%99%B3%E5%B0%8F%E5%A8%9F%E4%BF%BE%E8%B6%B3%E7%89%87%E9%85%AC%E5%86%8D%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C-%E9%BB%83%E7%A7%8B%E7%94%9F%EF%BC%9A%E5%88%86%E7%B4%85%E6%90%B5%E4%BB%B2%E5%A4%9A-171633\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25A8%259F%25E4%25BF%25BE%25E8%25B6%25B3%25E7%2589%2587%25E9%2585%25AC%25E5%2586%258D%25E5%2590%2588%25E4%25BD%259C-%25E9%25BB%2583%25E7%25A7%258B%25E7%2594%259F%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%2588%2586%25E7%25B4%2585%25E6%2590%25B5%25E4%25BB%25B2%25E5%25A4%259A-171633&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HPUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=da952a9e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/%E9%99%B3%E5%B0%8F%E5%A8%9F%E4%BF%BE%E8%B6%B3%E7%89%87%E9%85%AC%E5%86%8D%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C-%E9%BB%83%E7%A7%8B%E7%94%9F%EF%BC%9A%E5%88%86%E7%B4%85%E6%90%B5%E4%BB%B2%E5%A4%9A-171633</a></span><br />\n<br />\n陳小娟俾足片酬再合作 黃秋生：分紅搵仲多<br />\n10 小時前<br />\n<br />\n由導演陳小娟執導、黃秋生及菲籍女演員姬素．孔尚治(Crisel Consunji)主演的《淪落人》，不但在香港奪得多個獎項，更在意大利的《烏甸尼遠東電影節》奪得多個項，黃秋生等人獲獎後昨日返抵香港，他說日後或以分紅形式，來代替片酬。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《淪落人》這次獲得「觀眾票選金桑獎」(Golden Mulberry Audience Award)及「影評人黑龍大獎」(Black Dragon Award)，黃秋生更憑此片獲頒「傑出成就金桑獎」合共3個獎項。在抵港大堂接受訪問時，黃秋生說：「大會現場有句宣傳口號，意思類似係為皇帝鼓掌，得獎時三層樓都坐滿人一齊鼓掌，以前從未試過，感覺係用感動，都唔能夠形容到當時嘅感受。」陳小娟指，頒獎禮於當地晚上12時30分完成，所有儀式完畢已是凌晨2時，又大爆黃秋生得獎時非常緊張和眼濕濕，他聞言即說：「你睇到咩？不過真係有啲啲，我估應該係眼太乾！」<br />\n<br />\n鼓勵演員選擇分紅制<br />\n問到陳小娟會否與黃秋生在合作，她稱：「有機會！而且會俾足片酬。」<strong>黃秋生即說：「呢啲將來嘅事我點知呀，或者我紅咗唔理佢呢！(是否會收足片酬？)我覺得分紅呢個方法較好，我唔貪心，有3,000萬票房，我收得仲多錢，新導演同演員可以試一試咁樣嘅合作形式，自己博下，如果覺得套戲唔得，拍嚟把鬼咩？」</strong>"},{"pid":"8a0d537fdc2499d18d0961c8f644532f9e7911bb","tid":1142663,"uid":211461,"like":5,"dislike":22,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T08:38:16.000Z","msg":"陳小娟搵我拍戲我唔收錢<br />\n上床當片酬就okay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2122d0359f812d1d6709bff69b973a43e0bb82f7","tid":1142663,"uid":49391,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T08:38:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KiZjOHz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKiZjOHz.gif&h=e8d72581&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"57bc0ae022c8135687af8d8e79930b54f1297061","tid":1142663,"uid":217275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2122d0359f812d1d6709bff69b973a43e0bb82f7","tid":1142663,"uid":49391,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T08:38:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KiZjOHz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKiZjOHz.gif&h=e8d72581&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T08:58:07.000Z","msg":"大飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83448cee6eecb6a1ec7f17c6dc987bee0ca211a9","tid":1142663,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T09:02:12.000Z","msg":"港產片都係收片酬穩陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d7e3bc7fd7c37d9095f4376bcefeb8ee7f12830","tid":1142663,"uid":173814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T09:06:09.000Z","msg":"或者我紅咗唔理佢呢！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkg